        },
        {
            "+content": "30 years ago, an unknown \"invasive alien species\" appeared, bringing the world to the brink of ruin. Humans and the invasive species are fighting for dominion, and although humanity has now barely secured its own safety, its world could collapse at any time. While people are terrified of death, they also turn a blind eye to the peril around them and live their everyday lives. Amidst this, the \"United Nations Investigation Agency EXCEEDS\" works to combat invasive species and disasters. On the island country Mizuho in the far east, on an isolated island, lives Shiina Kuze. She is a hunter whose job it is to eradicate the invasive species on the island, and she wishes to live a quiet life with her sister, Setsuna.",
            "+@gid": "2588621832",
